{"tid":419964,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友有女朋友但鍾意左第二個女仔 點算？","createTime":"2017-10-01T03:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T22:12:00.000Z","uid":27731,"like":83,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ba77b5cf150565ff5e55b01f0556d4030644eb2f","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"講明先我朋友不是我<br />\n<br />\n佢有個拍拖好多年女朋友(5年以上) 冇聽過佢地有嘈過交感情好好，個女仔好乖又唔港女，樣都唔差，食飯AA家務煮飯整甜品樣樣得 ，仲要初戀黎 諗住都結硬婚。但自從條友仔返左新工識左個女仔(樣靚身材正)，比條女迷到失哂暈，個條女好似明知我朋友有個拍好耐拖既女友都照溝我朋友，搞到我朋友對女朋友好冷漠，又唔想見面電話又唔點覆，一日到黑都諗住個條女(聽佢講條女成日去飲野又食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，在我睇佢係比新鮮感蒙蔽左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟可以點屌醒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫佢同現任分手，趁早放過個好女仔，由佢仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勸下佢，同新女無好結果，有個咁好女朋友唔好破壞咁多年感情"},{"pid":"dd4fc831077d223d58f3f1a7cc4063662b99fc5d","tid":419964,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77d394677621aebbdc379f1f46fce1b9a46e81b4","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好成日發癲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  A0死毒撚 日撚日係到ff識到女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到底你真人係咪唔會出街 ？ 隱青果堆？</blockquote><br />\n做乜撚呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吔屎啦"},{"pid":"a768d45ed0e1c0718efe9c2455a242aa84cfe5c8","tid":419964,"uid":11893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"比人迷到傻撚左仲點會聽人勸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2164fb020a228218973ee5d1902b2304476e7f4d","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比人迷到傻撚左仲點會聽人勸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 唔想睇住佢後悔 呢對情侶我兩個都識 唔敢想像分左手佢女朋友會做咩傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e495bf53554dcb6edc2c537fe0af08b747be28","tid":419964,"uid":146968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"直接打佢一巴 屌醒佢 唔係佢一定後悔"},{"pid":"676355e0ab8649bfb642b7533150a291ece7a9c8","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接打佢一巴 屌醒佢 唔係佢一定後悔</blockquote><br />\n家陣佢日日返工同條新女對住，我車佢一巴實比佢開拖"},{"pid":"8b82440808a9abc4feefbbad0bc3692a5647bb4f","tid":419964,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"食左佢條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3161e62d49a56a8ff77bedae847b2f35be011715","tid":419964,"uid":140696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左佢條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者食左條新女"},{"pid":"492ca70df4d28ce8aa50e6c0e446928c3337e131","tid":419964,"uid":18616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:24:56.000Z","msg":"扼正皮.........."},{"pid":"c17494407f3692823293f0c2b4f698adc1f75044","tid":419964,"uid":91069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"叫佢死左佢啦"},{"pid":"5b49c6973d5dbd8a4530e6fe63d166ea6d600ac3","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左佢條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無所謂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賢妻良母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985be89e16dcc6645b63503061c9e6139434ec70","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食左佢條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者食左條新女</blockquote><br />\n可以一戰 發展不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106b137b56537b2a36a82691396daa7845d6b954","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扼正皮..........</blockquote><br />\n其實真心講句。。唔想見到佢咁傻 有d野錯左返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"0465a6f4f2453c5e8106dd1ba90899f31991c86e","tid":419964,"uid":2903,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"你係朋友,真心為個女仔就同佢講<br />\n而唔係由佢俾個男嘅呃住<br />\n到時候佢自己會知係男嘅錯而散<br />\n而唔係自己嘅錯"},{"pid":"875d094b77c791fc349a89561c709a3d9f5bc437","tid":419964,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:33:43.000Z","msg":"移情別戀關外人乜事"},{"pid":"e485b0847745133da55a37bcb46730b8156a4713","tid":419964,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"最不可靠是愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算身邊另一邊各方面都好好 但人就係唔知足"},{"pid":"aafe2948d752c02148875159cae4f343b9db5f81","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係朋友,真心為個女仔就同佢講<br />\n而唔係由佢俾個男嘅呃住<br />\n到時候佢自己會知係男嘅錯而散<br />\n而唔係自己嘅錯</blockquote><br />\n咁又未去到出軌。。仲有得救既。。"},{"pid":"af8811440a04b98b9412216d0cf7fc723dcd7c19","tid":419964,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bfbb608550758af1605f851e8c5417c0bcebe7","tid":419964,"uid":27731,"like":0,